General.Name: Nidaros Sparebank
General.Description: Nidaros Sparebank, a savings bank, provides loans, savings, insurance, pension products, and payment services for private and corporate customers in Norway. The company offers online banking services. Nidaros Sparebank was founded in 1858 and is based in Klæbu, Norway.
